SAN FRANCISCO, March 9, 2004  The Board of Directors of ABM Industries Incorporated (NYSE: ABM) has declared an all-time-high second quarter cash dividend of $0.10 per common share payable on May 3, 2004 to stockholders of record on April 12, 2004. This will be ABM's 152 consecutive quarterly cash dividend, and is $0.005 (5.3%) above the $0.095 per share quarterly dividend rate paid in 2003.
