          1.      The Company hereby grants to the Employee a non-qualified stock option to purchase shares of the Common Stock at the price set forth in Paragraph 2, on the terms and conditions hereinafter stated. In consideration of the grant of this option and the other rights which are being concurrently granted to him, the Employee hereby agrees to continue in the employment of the Company for a period of at least one year from the date of grant of this option.
