     1.1 . Subject to the terms and conditions of this Agreement, in accordance with the Delaware Limited Liability Company Act (the "") and the Belize International Business Companies Act (the ""), at the Effective Time, Target will merge with and into Merger Sub. Merger Sub will be the surviving company in the Merger and will continue its limited liability company existence under the laws of the State of Delaware. As of the Effective Time, the separate corporate existence of Target under the laws of Belize will cease.
