     4.5 . None of Parent, any Parent Subsidiary or any of their respective officers or directors has employed any broker, finder or financial advisor or incurred any liability for any brokers fees, commissions or financial advisory or finder's fees in connection with the Merger or related transactions contemplated by this Agreement, other than Lazard Frres & Co. LLC.
