Note 5  Short-term / long-term restricted cash deposits
 
The Group has pledged certain cash deposits to support its self-insurance program (note 12). In view of the restriction as to the use and availability of the cash deposits to the Group, the balance cannot be classified as a cash and cash equivalent and it has therefore been classified within current assets and non-current assets in accordance with its terms. Classification of restricted cash between short-term and long-term is based upon current and future insurance payouts as projected by the Group's consulting actuary.
