NEW YORK  September 4, 2008  The Board of Directors of ABM Industries Incorporated (NYSE: ABM) has declared a fourth quarter cash dividend of $0.125 per common share payable on November 3, 2008 to stockholders of record on October 9, 2008. This will be ABM's 170 consecutive quarterly cash dividend, and is $0.005 (4.2%) above the $0.12 per share quarterly dividend rate declared and paid for the fourth quarter of 2007.
