     (e) On December 9, 2008, the Board approved amendments to the Executive Stock Option Plan (aka Age-Vested Career Stock Option Plan), as amended and restated as of September 4, 2007, to provide for accelerated vesting of stock options in the event of a change in control of the Company upon the terms and conditions set forth therein.
