Item 8.01. Other Events
On November 1, 2012, the Company completed the acquisition of all of the outstanding shares of Air Serv Corporation ("Air Serv"). On October 8, 2012, the Company announced that it had entered into an agreement to purchase Air Serv for approximately $158 million in cash, subject to certain closing adjustments. Founded in 2002, Air Serv employs approximately 12,000 employees worldwide and is a leading provider of integrated facility management services for the world's leading airlines and freight companies at airports throughout the United States and United Kingdom.
